OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fstart but cloud and showery rain in
OL,7,Fthe west will move east across all
OL,8,Fparts. Becoming dry with clear spells
OL,9,Fafter midnight with patchy frost
OL,10,Finland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FA cold start to the day with
OL,13,Fa frost for some places. It will
OL,14,Fremain dry with plenty of sunshine but
OL,15,Fperhaps some high cloud spreading east
OL,16,Fin the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
