OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FVariable cloud and bright spells with
OL,7,Fsome outbreaks of rain on Wednesday.
OL,8,FRain bands moving east on Thursday
OL,9,Ffollowed by drier, brighter spells for
OL,10,Fthe rest of the week.
